             was indicted for <rs id="t18320216-41-off221" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320216-41-off221" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320216-41-off221" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
