                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320216-41-off221 t18320216-41-cd222"></join>, 8 pairs of gloves, value 6s.; 1 night-cap, value 6d.; 1 handkerchief, value 1s.; 2 sovereigns, 1 half-sovereign, and 5 half-crowns, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320216-41-victim411" type="victimName">
